original_title: Atoms For Peace Live London's Roundhouse 2013
overview: Atoms for Peace live at London's Roundhouse on 25th July 2013.  Setlist : Before Your Very Eyes, Default, The Clock, Ingenue, Stuck Together Pieces, Unless, And It Rained All Night, Harrowdown Hill, Dropped, Cymbal Rush.  Encore: The Hollow Earth, Feeling Pulled Apart by Horses, Rabbit in Your Headlights, Amok.  Encore 2: Atoms for Peace, Paperbag Writer, Black Swan.
